# Rain Monitor 03

## Purpose

Made for Assignment 1 of [CIS 5120: Human-Computer Interaction](https://cis4120.seas.upenn.edu/) taught by Professor DanaÃ« Metaxa.

Allows users to track three critical weather metrics: temperature, humidity, and precipitation, with ample history accessible through simple horizontal swipes.

## Installation

Get [bun](https://bun.sh/) and run `bun install`, then `bun dev`

